text:
Hello,
I would like to send you my application for a job in the Hellfest. It would be my dream to work for you as any of the jobs that you can ask me to do. I am easy going, flexible, sociable, smiling and efficient. Furthermore, it would bring me experiences that I could put in my resume. The Hellfest is such an amazing and famous festival. I came, once, during the beginning of summer and I particularly loved the architecture and the atmosphere. Moreover, the scene, the artists and the arts were amazing and I am going to remember every details of this weekend during my all life. The favourite work of arts that was striking me was the white skeleton head with gold butterflies. I enjoyed it very much.
However my feelings for your festival, I think I would be really helpful and that this experience can make me growing up so fast ! It would also be my pleasure to work for you and it would confort me, or not, in my choice of studies.
I don't need to be paid for this job. I just want to be a part of this organisation, which is so big and famous. For me, it is the best festival of the world, and I am not saying that to be accepted. It mixes work of arts, music and a special event at the same time.
I think I am perfect to help you because, as an student in communication, I know how to use some of the new technologies, how to have the perfect communication and which media is the most interesting to be published on. Knowing my young age, I have a young looking and a young point of view on which communication is better for young people. As far as I am concerned, I think I could be an important element in your teamwork with a fresh looking. For example I think if you want to bring younger people, you can increase your communication and publicity on Tik tok because this social media is very using by teenagers.
Finally, since I know that I would work in festival, my dream has always been to work for the Hellfest. Even if I am not considering myself as a rock and metal fan, I really enjoy the atmosphere of the Hellfest and I think I would become more mature thanks to this experience. I am a huge fan of what you have created and I always will be.
I am looking forward to hear about you,
Best regards
